1254
01:55:23,958 --> 01:55:26.291
Amar had an appointment today,
with the doctor.

1255
01:55:26,916 --> 01:55:28.791
I remembered just
after I dropped you home.

1256
01:55:28,916 --> 01:55:30.333
I went straight to Amar's house.

1257
01:55:30,416 --> 01:55:32.625
