1290
01:57:57,125 --> 01:57:59.125
Let's not speak in front of her,
it'll upset her.

1291
01:58:42,583 --> 01:58:43.875
Hi, Taran.

1292
01:58:45,125 --> 01:58:45.916
Hi.

1293
01:58:52,458 --> 01:58:54.500
- Gurpreet..come on.
- Sorry..

1294
01:58:54,875 --> 01:58:58.833
Sorry, my friend came over and..

1295
01:58:59,166 --> 01:59:00.916
..we went out to watch the game.

1296
01:59:01,750 --> 01:59:03.291
We had some beer.

1297
01:59:09,541 --> 01:59:10.666
Where is Amar?

1298
01:59:12,083 --> 01:59:13.083
Where's Amar?

1299
01:59:16,958 --> 01:59:18.791
Aahh..he sleeps early.

1300
01:59:19,791 --> 01:59:21.458
Did he take his meds?

1301
01:59:22,083 --> 01:59:23.958
Did he?

1302
01:59:26,208 --> 01:59:27.708
He must have.

1303
01:59:28,833 --> 01:59:33.125
Anyway, I think it's quite late,
we should get going.

1304
01:59:36,500 --> 01:59:39.166
I am okay.
I am fine.

1305
01:59:39,375 --> 01:59:41.750
- You're not fine.
- I am fine.

1306
01:59:41,916 --> 01:59:43.833
- Not fine.
- I said I am fine!

1307
01:59:44,541 --> 01:59:45.875
- I am fine.
- Shekhar, enough.

1308
01:59:46,250 --> 01:59:47.583
Enough what, Taran?

1309
01:59:48,541 --> 01:59:49.541
Enough what?

1310
01:59:49,708 --> 01:59:51.541
I want to tell you enough.

1311
01:59:51,791 --> 01:59:53.750
Did I tell you to love me?

1312
01:59:54,041 --> 01:59:56.708
Did I tell you not to love Amar?

1313
01:59:57,250 --> 02:00:01.791
But..you told Amar, that you love me.

1314
02:00:02,541 --> 02:00:03.500
Yes.

1315
02:00:05,541 --> 02:00:06.125
I did.

1316
02:00:06,500 --> 02:00:07.291
Yeah..

1317
02:00:09,416 --> 02:00:11.166
Come on,
Shekhar..let's talk tomorrow.

1318
02:00:11,625 --> 02:00:12.916
I don't want to talk.

1319
02:00:14,125 --> 02:00:15.125
I am going.

1320
02:00:16,250 --> 02:00:17.541
Forever.

1321
02:00:18,666 --> 02:00:21.458
- Shekhar, let's..
- I said I don't want to talk.

1322
02:00:21,541 --> 02:00:24.541
Enough, son.
That's enough for today.

1323
02:00:25,541 --> 02:00:27.541
You want to go home, go home.

1324
02:00:28,625 --> 02:00:30.291
You can speak with Taran tomorrow.

1325
02:00:37,541 --> 02:00:38.416
Shekhar.

1326
02:00:41,458 --> 02:00:42.333
Brother..

1327
02:01:07,875 --> 02:01:09.375
He's not that kind of a guy.

1328
02:01:10,250 --> 02:01:11.583
I can't believe this.

1329
02:01:13,041 --> 02:01:13.750
I know.

1330
02:01:52,583 --> 02:01:54.041
Who is Shekhar, Taran?

1331
02:02:00,625 --> 02:02:02.458
He's not the son of my friend.

1332
02:02:04,916 --> 02:02:05.875
I lied.

1333
02:02:13,458 --> 02:02:15.291
He suddenly showed
up one day out of nowhere.

1334
02:02:22,666 --> 02:02:25.208
Both of us were in a place
where we shouldn't have been.

1335
02:02:34,750 --> 02:02:36.625
It wasn't his fault either, sir.

1336
02:02:38,000 --> 02:02:39.333
Nor was it mine.

1337
02:02:53,291 --> 02:02:56.791
I was right behind you two
when you were looking for him.

1338
02:02:59,416 --> 02:03:00.583
Waiting..

1339
02:03:02,250 --> 02:03:03.708
I was waiting too..

1340
02:03:05,291 --> 02:03:06.458
..for Amar to be found.

1341
02:03:08,125 --> 02:03:10.125
And get this big load off my chest.

1342
02:03:11,416 --> 02:03:13.625
Truth takes up a lot
of space in your heart, sir.

1343
02:03:15,583 --> 02:03:16.625
There's no way to accommodate it.

1344
02:03:23,833 --> 02:03:24.958
I couldn't take it anymore.

1345
02:03:26,166 --> 02:03:29.125
I thought I should tell you the truth.

1346
02:03:31,250 --> 02:03:32.875
Unwillingly..

1347
02:03:34,333 --> 02:03:37.250
..I snatched the most valuable thing
from yours and Taran's life.

1348
02:03:39,958 --> 02:03:41.375
I have no one..

1349
02:03:42,250 --> 02:03:43.416
..so I'll do whatever you say.

1350
02:03:45,958 --> 02:03:47.375
Take me to the police.

1351
02:03:48,333 --> 02:03:49.708
Kill me.

1352
02:03:51,083 --> 02:03:52.208
Make me your slave.

1353
02:03:55,250 --> 02:03:56.708
Or make me your son!

1354
02:04:06,125 --> 02:04:08.458
He had no reason to come here.

1355
02:04:09,458 --> 02:04:10.833
To tell the truth.

1356
02:04:13,666 --> 02:04:15.958
But from what I saw in his eyes..

1357
02:04:18,000 --> 02:04:20.541
..I felt he can be trusted.

1358
02:04:34,375 --> 02:04:35.250
All of us were..

1359
02:04:37,041 --> 02:04:41.208
..trying to deal with your accident,
in our own ways.

1360
02:04:45,583 --> 02:04:47.625
He wanted to deal with it too.

1361
02:04:50,208 --> 02:04:51.875
He wanted to help me.

1362
02:04:56,916 --> 02:04:59.208
But in a way,
he was asking for my help too.

1363
02:05:01,625 --> 02:05:03.916
In the beginning,
I would take him to the office.

1364
02:05:05,958 --> 02:05:09.916
In the evenings,
he would drop by for some coffee.

1365
02:05:10,250 --> 02:05:10.833
'Shekhar.'

1366
02:05:11,041 --> 02:05:12.041
- 'Hi.
- Hi.'

1367
02:05:19,000 --> 02:05:23.000
I didn't realize..when he
became more like a son to me.

1368
02:05:50,041 --> 02:05:51.458
You can't find him now, son.

1369
02:06:22,291 --> 02:06:24.875
You're ok, you're fine.

1370
02:06:25,333 --> 02:06:26.958
Careful.

1371
02:07:02,666 --> 02:07:05.666
It's just this wound over
my left eye that hurts, otherwise..

1372
02:07:05,791 --> 02:07:07.541
Do you have any clue
how drunk you are?

1373
02:07:08,000 --> 02:07:09.583
And who drives after getting so high?

1374
02:07:09,875 --> 02:07:11.333
Are you a doctor or a cop?

1375
02:07:11,625 --> 02:07:12.750
Just do your job.

1376
02:07:19,166 --> 02:07:20.500
What are you doing?

1377
02:07:21,750 --> 02:07:23.416
You're hurting that poor girl.

1378
02:07:24,250 --> 02:07:25.750
A little pain now..

1379
02:07:28,041 --> 02:07:29.875
..will save her from
a lifetime of anguish.

1380
02:07:31,375 --> 02:07:33.000
Let me go, please.

1381
02:07:34,916 --> 02:07:36.583
You don't love her?

1382
02:07:39,791 --> 02:07:41.875
Love is not some relationship.

1383
02:07:44,333 --> 02:07:47.875
It's a ray of light
which offers a glimpse of God.

1384
02:07:50,583 --> 02:07:53.041
And I am listening to my God now.

1385
02:08:43,625 --> 02:08:44.750
- Hello, sir.
- Hi.

1386
02:08:44,958 --> 02:08:46.250
The aircraft is ready, sir.

1387
02:08:46,291 --> 02:08:48.416
Should be able to take
off in about 15 minutes.

1388
02:08:49,666 --> 02:08:51.208
I want to meet him.

1389
02:08:52,625 --> 02:08:55.125
I want him to tell
me what my fault was.

1390
02:08:55,625 --> 02:08:57.416
And then he can go
wherever he wants to.

1391
02:08:58,333 --> 02:09:00.500
- Taran..
- I want to meet him.

1392
02:09:00,958 --> 02:09:04.000
He can't do this. I want to meet him.

1393
02:09:04,416 --> 02:09:05.208
But..

1394
02:09:05,333 --> 02:09:07.416
He will take off in 15 minutes.

1395
02:09:09,708 --> 02:09:13.375
I don't know where he is going.

1396
02:09:15,958 --> 02:09:18.541
There's no chance of
getting there in 15 minutes.

1397
02:09:19,083 --> 02:09:20.458
- Traffic..
- Harry..

1398
02:09:20,666 --> 02:09:21.541
Can't make it.

1399
02:09:23,208 --> 02:09:25.333
Taran's question is important.

1400
02:09:26,208 --> 02:09:28.291
I will get her there in 15 minutes.

1401
02:09:28,500 --> 02:09:30.458
But I need your help, please.

1402
02:10:48,333 --> 02:10:49.166
Shekhar.

1403
02:11:09,625 --> 02:11:12.000
Don't do this to her.

1404
02:11:16,000 --> 02:11:17.750
First she grieved for me..

1405
02:11:19,125 --> 02:11:20.583
..now she will grieve for you.

1406
02:11:21,416 --> 02:11:24.708
Please..what is her fault?

1407
02:11:33,875 --> 02:11:34.958
I know..

1408
02:11:36,458 --> 02:11:38.166
..who you are.

1409
02:11:39,083 --> 02:11:40.291
We all do.

1410
02:11:43,125 --> 02:11:45.375
But we still love you.

1411
02:11:54,000 --> 02:11:55.666
That's the problem..

1412
02:11:57,833 --> 02:11:59.250
..everyone loves me.

1413
02:12:02,000 --> 02:12:03.541
Otherwise it was so easy.

1414
02:12:04,375 --> 02:12:08.708
I would've quietly escaped..

1415
02:12:09,125 --> 02:12:10.416
..to my world.

1416
02:12:19,666 --> 02:12:21.291
Why did you show up again?

1417
02:12:22,708 --> 02:12:24.625
You made this all the
more difficult for me to leave.

1418
02:12:25,541 --> 02:12:26.875
Why do you want to go, Shekhar?

1419
02:12:27,750 --> 02:12:29.916
You had your own
world before I arrived.

1420
02:12:30,333 --> 02:12:32.291
And now you have that back.

1421
02:12:33,916 --> 02:12:35.916
And there's no place
for Shekhar in that world.

1422
02:12:36,625 --> 02:12:39.125
Will you decide whom I love?

1423
02:12:41,458 --> 02:12:46.583
Only I have that
right.. me.. not you.

1424
02:12:48,125 --> 02:12:50.041
If I had that right..

1425
02:12:52,208 --> 02:12:54.416
..then you could've
never loved someone else.

1426
02:12:55,875 --> 02:12:59.250
Not now..or in the next
lifetime..or after that.

1427
02:13:00,625 --> 02:13:01.625
Then why?

1428
02:13:04,375 --> 02:13:06.083
I just want to tell you..

1429
02:13:06,333 --> 02:13:12.583
What you're doing is completely
different from what you want, Taran.

1430
02:13:13,125 --> 02:13:15.333
You didn't do anything wrong, Taran.

1431
02:13:16,000 --> 02:13:21.000
The other day, in the temple,
when I asked you why you chose me..

1432
02:13:22,333 --> 02:13:25.666
..you said 'I am
doing the right thing'.

1433
02:13:28,625 --> 02:13:30.833
It's true that it's not my fault.

1434
02:13:32,666 --> 02:13:34.583
Also true that I love you.

1435
02:13:40,000 --> 02:13:41.958
Maybe more..

1436
02:13:43,875 --> 02:13:45.708
..than you know.

1437
02:13:49,291 --> 02:13:52.583
But not more than you love Amar.

1438
02:13:55,750 --> 02:13:57.625
Love is not some
responsibility, Taran.

1439
02:13:59,625 --> 02:14:01.000
Love is not reasonable.

1440
02:14:02,125 --> 02:14:03.833
It just happens.

1441
02:14:04,291 --> 02:14:05.875
Only compromises are reasonable.

1442
02:14:08,208 --> 02:14:09.291
Fine, I won't go.

1443
02:14:13,166 --> 02:14:15.375
Look into my eye and say..

1444
02:14:16,541 --> 02:14:18.041
..that you don't love Amar.

1445
02:14:21,208 --> 02:14:24.750
Say that every day you didn't
feel something shatter inside you..

1446
02:14:25,208 --> 02:14:27.291
..after you told Amar about me.

1447
02:14:33,458 --> 02:14:35.291
Say it Taran, and I won't go.

1448
02:14:37,833 --> 02:14:38.833
Say it..

1449
02:14:47,375 --> 02:14:49.416
Don't do the right thing, silly..

1450
02:14:50,875 --> 02:14:52.083
..fall in love.

1451
02:14:59,333 --> 02:15:00.916
It's my turn to do the right thing.

1452
02:15:04,291 --> 02:15:05.166
See you.

1453
02:15:40,208 --> 02:15:43.291
Smile..laugh..be happy..

1454
02:15:46,083 --> 02:15:46.875
Love..!
